            <div class="row">
                <div class="span12">
                    

<p class="leader">Starting October 1st, millions of Americans will
                    have access to affordable care through the new health insurance marketplace.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="span6">
                    

<div class="get-facts">
	<h3><em>get</em> THE FACTS</h3>
	<p>
		 If you have health insurance and you like it, you can keep itâ€”and you&rsquo;re already getting benefits because of Obamacare:
	</p>
	<ol>
		<li>
		<p>
			 Free preventive care, including check&mdash;ups and vaccinations
		</p>
		 </li>
		<li>
		<p>
			 Money back if your insurance company doesn&rsquo;t spend at least 80% of your premium on care
		</p>
		 </li>
		<li>
		<p>
			 No more lifetime limits on how much your insurance company will pay for
		</p>
		 </li>
		<li>
		<p>
			 Children and young adults can stay on their family plans until they turn 26
		</p>
		 </li>
	</ol>
	 <a class="button blue" href="/health-care/facts">LEARN MORE</a>
</div>

                </div>
                <div class="span6">
                    

<div class="get-coverd">
	<h3><em>get</em> COVERED</h3>
	<div class="col-border">
		<p>
			    If you&rsquo;re one of the millions of Americans who doesn&rsquo;t have health insurance&mdash;or if you purchase health insurance on your own or for your small business&mdash;you now have the chance to get quality care that you can afford.
		</p>
		<form class="well page-form signup" method="post" id="ala-options" action="https://my.barackobama.com/page/s/helthcare-info-request">
			<h4>GET MORE HEALTH CARE INFORMATION:</h4>
			<ol>
				<li class="email"><input name="email" id="email" placeholder="Email"></li>
				<li class="zip"><input name="zip" id="zip" type="text" placeholder="ZIP"></li>
				<li class="button"><button class="blue" type="submit">SHOW MY OPTIONS</button></li>
			</ol>
			<input name="bp_load_counter" type="hidden" value="1"><input name="redirect_url" type="hidden">
		</form>
		<ol>
			<li>
			<p>
				    Millions of Americans will be eligible for financial assistance
			</p>
			</li>
			<li>
			<p>
				    You can&rsquo;t be denied coverage, no matter what
			</p>
			</li>
			<li>
			<p>
				    Choose the plan that&rsquo;s right for you
			</p>
			</li>
			<li>
			<p>
				    Sign up any time between October 2013 and March 2014
			</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</div>
</div>

                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
